<author>ạlạ̉b fạdy jndḥ, sẖạrl sẖlạlạ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tnʿysẖ ạlsmạ ʿạlạ̉rḍ
 bdạ mnk rgẖbẗ qlb
 whạlrgẖbh ttnmạ fyk
 slm ḥyạtk llrb
 nạṭr mn qlbk yswʿ
 ʿn qlbw mạ tbqy̱ bʿyd
 blmsh bysẖfy jrwḥạtk
 wbḥwl ḥznk lʿyd
 wbtmḍy ạlạ̹yạm wbtbqy̱ ạ̹nt ạ̹nt
 mạ btnʿs mạ btnạm btshr ʿqlby ạ̹nt
 rgẖbẗ qlby ạlywm ṣyr ạ̹nsạn jdyd
 ạ̹htf bqlb ạlʿạlm ạ̹nt frḥy ạlwḥyd
 yswʿ frḥy
 2- tnʿysẖ ạlsmạ ʿạlạ̉rḍ
 bdạ mnk qwẗ wḥb
 whạlqwẗ ttkbr fyk
 slm kl ḍʿfk llrb
 nạṭr ʿbạbk yswʿ
 ʿn drbw mạ trwḥ bʿyd
 lḥbw qlbk byjwʿ
 tʿạ lʿndw mn jdyd
 wbtmḍy ạlạ̹yạm wbtbqy̱ ạ̹nt ạ̹nt
 mạ btnʿs mạ btnạm btshr ʿqlby ạ̹nt
 rgẖbẗ qlby ạlywm ṣyr ạ̹nsạn jdyd
 ạ̹htf bqlb ạlʿạlm ạ̹nt frḥy ạlwḥyd
 yswʿ frḥy</lyrics>
<title>tnʿysẖ ạlsmạ ʿạlạ̉rḍ</title>
</song>